SELECT * FROM "common"."permissions_chameleon" LIMIT 10
SELECT * FROM "common"."permissions" LIMIT 10
SELECT * FROM "common"."user_chameleon" LIMIT 5
SELECT column_name, data_type, is_nullable, column_default FROM information_schema.columns WHERE table_schema = 'common' AND table_name = 'permissions_chameleon' ORDER BY ordinal_position
SELECT table_name FROM information_schema.tables WHERE table_schema = 'common' AND table_name LIKE '%chameleon%' OR table_name LIKE '%permission%'
SELECT column_name, data_type, is_nullable, column_default FROM information_schema.columns WHERE table_schema = 'common' AND table_name = 'permission_groups' ORDER BY ordinal_position
SELECT column_name, data_type, is_nullable, column_default FROM information_schema.columns WHERE table_schema = 'common' AND table_name = 'permissions' ORDER BY ordinal_position
SELECT column_name, data_type, is_nullable, column_default FROM information_schema.columns WHERE table_schema = 'common' AND table_name = 'user_chameleon' ORDER BY ordinal_position
SELECT type_id, type, value, level_above, is_deleted, order_by FROM nursing.event_type ORDER BY type_id
SELECT * FROM common.room_type_details LIMIT 20
SELECT * FROM common.room_type LIMIT 20
SELECT DISTINCT sw.room_id, r.room_desc FROM patients.surgery_waiting sw LEFT JOIN patients.rooms r ON sw.room_id = r.room_id WHERE sw.room_id IS NOT NULL AND sw.room_id <> '' ORDER BY sw.room_id
SELECT room_id, room_desc, ward_id FROM patients.rooms WHERE room_id LIKE 'פז%' OR room_desc LIKE '%ניתוח%' LIMIT 20
SELECT category_id, category_desc, category_long_desc FROM common.ward_category WHERE category_id IN (7, 8, 20, 23, 24, 25, 26) ORDER BY category_id

SELECT ward_id, ward_desc, category_id FROM common.wards w LEFT JOIN common.ward_category wc ON w.ward_category = wc.category_id WHERE wc.category_id IN (8, 20) OR ward_desc LIKE '%ניתוח%' OR ward_desc LIKE '%חדר%' LIMIT 20
SELECT * FROM patients.patients_in_surgery LIMIT 5

SELECT sw.case_id, sw.priority_code, sw.priority_desc, sw.procedure_desc, sw.room_id, c.nursing_ward FROM patients.surgery_waiting sw JOIN patients.cases c ON sw.case_id = c.case_id WHERE c.is_active = true LIMIT 10
